      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 29:9",
      "source_id": "kjv",
      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/eng-kjv2006/PSA029.htm",
      "text": "The voice of the LORD maketh the hinds to calve, and discovereth the forests: and in his temple doth every one speak of [his] glory.",
      "versionTitle": "King James Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 29:9",
      "source_id": "asv",
      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/eng-asv/PSA029.htm",
      "text": "The voice of Jehovah maketh the hinds to calve, And strippeth the forests bare: And in his temple everything saith, Glory.",
      "versionTitle": "American Standard Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 29:9",
      "source_id": "web",
      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/engwebp/PSA029.htm",
      "text": "The LORD’s voice makes the deer calve, and strips the forests bare. In his temple everything says, “Glory!”",
